Interface DataSourceJdbc

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataSource, DbSynchUnitAbstract, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataSourceJdbcImpl

    public interface DataSourceJdbc
extends DataSource
    A representation of the model object 'Data Source Jdbc'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Data Base User
    • Data Base User Pwd
    • Default Schema
